    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm really busy with work this week and my doctor's office is closed until monday. i really need to finish this antibiotic to get over this sinus thing or i won't be able to work. is there any way i can just stagger them, like taking the simvastatin at night and the antibiotic in the morning? would that make it safe enough so i don't have to wait until monday to deal with it?",
